name: Lakeyah
description: '''Lakeyah Danaee Robinson''' (born February 28, 2001), known mononymously as '''Lakeyah''', is an American rapper, singer, and television personality. Born and raised in [[Milwaukee]], she began recording at the age of 15. At 18, she moved to [[Atlanta]] and was signed to [[Quality Control Music]]. She was part of the [[XXL (magazine)|''XXL'' magazine]] 2021 freshman class, as the first inductee to hail from Milwaukee.
